      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOLDSTAR HECTOR (6) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing 28 from 42 starts. Finished second (22.02) at this track last time making it three minors on end. Top prospect. MAYWYN'S QUEEN (8) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when second (22.24) at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expecting another good run. BONES (2) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 1.3 lengths at this track in a handy 20.13 beating Magic Mystery. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Shapes as a top winning chance on latest effort. MY BOY TWIST (1) will have admirers after surprising many with a placing last time out.",
